import { createApp } from 'vue'
import './input.css'
import App from './App.vue'
import { createRouter, createWebHistory } from 'vue-router'
import axios from 'axios';
import 'flowbite/dist/flowbite.css';

import DashboardPage from './components/DashboardPage.vue'
import LoginPage from './components/LoginPage.vue'
import TestPage from './components/TestPage.vue'
import YoutubePage from './components/item/YoutubePage.vue'
import ReunioMeter from './components/ReunioMeterPage.vue'
import WrongPage from './components/item/WrongPass.vue'
import Nf from './components/NotFound.vue'
import TypeFormsPage from './components/item/TypeFormsPage.vue'
import WeezEventPage from './components/item/WeezEventPage.vue'
import LinkedinPage from './components/item/LinkedInPage.vue'
import TwitterPage from './components/item/TwitterPage.vue'
import InstagramPage from './components/item/InstagramPage.vue'
import FacebookPage from './components/item/FacebookPage.vue'

const routes = [
    { path: process.env.VUE_APP_LOGIN, component: LoginPage },
    { path: process.env.VUE_APP_DASH, component: DashboardPage },
    { path: process.env.VUE_APP_TEST, component: TestPage },
    { path: process.env.VUE_APP_INSTA, component: InstagramPage },
    { path: process.env.VUE_APP_YOUTUBE, component: YoutubePage },
    { path: process.env.VUE_APP_METER, component: ReunioMeter },
    { path: process.env.VUE_APP_WPAS, component: WrongPage },
    { path: process.env.VUE_APP_404, component:Nf },
    { path: process.env.VUE_APP_TYPEFORMS, component: TypeFormsPage },
    { path: process.env.VUE_APP_WEEZEVENT, component: WeezEventPage },
    { path: process.env.VUE_APP_WEEZEVENT, component: LinkedinPage},
    { path: process.env.VUE_APP_TWITTER, component: TwitterPage},
    { path: process.env.VUE_APP_INSTAGRAM, component: InstagramPage},
    { path: process.env.VUE_APP_FACEBOOK, component: FacebookPage},
  ]

  const router = createRouter({
    history: createWebHistory(),
    routes,
    mode:'hash'
  })

  // app.config.globalProperties.$axios = axios;

  const app = createApp(App);
  app.config.globalProperties.$axios = axios;
  app.use(router).mount('#app');
